room_title: Escape room "The Lair of the Puzzlemaster" by Trapped! Escape Room Upland in Pomona
room_address: 600 N Mountain Ave b204, Upland, CA 91786
room_description: You are federal agents tracking the notorious international criminal known only as “The Puzzlemaster”. After several years of investigation, you have finally found his hidden lair. You are moving in to take him down, but now the question looms: have you trapped him, or has he trapped you?
